            <div class="case-info1">
                <h5>Problem</h5>
                <p class="c-info">Almost everyone has a hectic lifestyle, maintaining a good work-life balance isn’t
                    easy. Even finding the time to do what we enjoy can be tough, more so for something as little as
                    applying and re-applying sunscreen — even though it’s crucially important for our health.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="case-info2">
                <h5>Solution</h5>
                <p class="c-info">An app that reminds its users to apply sunscreen every morning, as well as reminding
                    the users to re-apply the sunscreen at certain intervals. Make it easy for the users to check the
                    time they applied the product and when they need to apply it again.</p>
            </div>
